components.name: Arm Cortex M0 N32G020 MCU

specification.description: N32G020 MCUs are based on 32-bit ARM Cortex-M0 core with a maximum operating frequency up to 80MHz. The series integrates up to 256K Flash, 20K SRAM, 1K Retention RAM, and up to 30 GPIOs, supports the following peripheral communication interfaces, 12-bit 1Msps SAR ADC, 10-bit DAC, analog comparator, RTC real-time clock, multi-channel complementary output PWM, USB2.0 (Full Speed) Device, multi-channel SPI, UART, I2C, ISO7816，and also integrates two-channel 3.3V LDO outputs. The Series equip with a variety of encryption algorithm hardware acceleration engine complying with international Standard. It can provide high-performance DES / 3DES, AES, SHA, RSA, ECC international algorithms, with multiple power consumption operating modes, of which PowerDown (Typ) is 0.1uA.
